title: Smash Bros' Newest Prodigy - The Story of Jmook

media:group.media:title: Smash Bros' Newest Prodigy - The Story of Jmook
media:group.media:description:
Super Smash Bros Melee has recently seen a lot of new talent emerge onto the scene. 

With an impressive tournament track record and professional work ethic, one player, in particular, has stood out as potentially one of the best in the world. 

This is the story of Jake "Jmook" DiRado, Smash Melee's newest prodigy that is looking to take the scene by storm.
